  • Shubhra Sharma sambhav sinaha ji, prakand gurudev ke hote hue main yahan apke prashan ka uttar dene main thoda jijhak rahee hoon parantu jo thoda bahut maine para hai uske anusar eshwar param satya aur pawan hain ,hum manushya kee trah unme balya awastha, yauvan awastha, vriddha awastha arthathatra awastha parivartan nahi hota ,eshwar aur unka roop shawasta hai, Deviyan param pavitra kauymarya kee prateek hain , sansarik manushya kee bhati srishti srijan ke liye unhe un sharik awastthon se nahi gujrana parta jinse sansarik estriyun ko.
    Waise bhee eshwar ka vastawik swaroop param jyoti punj hai.

    Yahi karan hai Eshwar ke dadi munch nahi hota aur Deviyan param kaumarya kee prateek hain.

    koi truti huee ho toh gurudev kshama karen aur trutiyun ko sudhar kar naveen gyan se alokit karen.
